room_title: Escape room "The Raid on Mr. Croft’s Museum" by Escape MKE in Milwaukee
room_address: 3333 N Mayfair Road Suite 314 Milwaukee, WI 53222
room_description: It has been rumored, billionaire antique collector John Croft holds one of the world’s richest collections of privately owned artifacts. You and your team of highly trained thieves have been hired by a rival antique collector, Alexander Ford, to penetrate Croft’s museum and steal his most prized possession, the staff of Tut.
